<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yemeni Socialist Party Offers Cease-Firea Plan </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    YSP Official on Conditions </H4>

<F P=102> JN1305195094 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1741 GMT 13 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN1305195094 </F>
