<F P=102>   EA1806133094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
in Arabic 2045 GMT 17 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA1806133094 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
in Arabic 2045 GMT 17 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
