<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yemeni Delegation Meets With al-Asad, Departs </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN2406163394 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1515 GMT 24 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN2406163394 </F>
